code: export default function reduce(values,reducer,value){if(typeof reducer!=="function")throw new TypeError("reducer is not a function");const iterator=values[Symbol.iterator]();let done,next,index=-1;if(arguments.length<3){({done,value}=iterator.next());if(done)return;++index;}while({done,value:next}=iterator.next(),!done){value=reducer(value,next,++index,values);}return value;}
